name: Sci-Fi Diffusion v1.0
description:
An early version of the upcoming generalist Sci-Fi model based on SD v2.X.

This model has been trained on 26,949 high resolution and quality Sci-Fi themed images for 2 Epochs. Which equals to around 53K steps/iterations. The training resolution was 640, however it works well at higher resolutions. This model is still in developement

Recommended Samplers:

- Euler
- Euler A
- DPM++ SDE Karras
